{"tid":1395751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急)我朋友話被姦嗰個女仔已經報咗警","createTime":"2019-08-02T00:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T00:48:45.000Z","uid":160887,"like":74,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"99c7f5a5797edb2517a666a1ac2f35bc11eddfa4","tid":1395751,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:29:15.000Z","msg":"屌你地班傻閪唔好係咩都信啦<br />\n<br />\n連登已經夠多假膠，telegram 呢啲仲要check唔到你過往講過啲咩嘅app傳出嚟嘅消息仲好信<br />\n<br />\n圖係可以改，錄音可以係假<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁冇圖冇錄音嘅文字</span></span><br />\n你仲會信?<br />\n會唔會咁戇鳩呀<br />\n<br />\n得閒用下你個死人腦，唔好係有傳唔係有傳<br />\n思考嗰件事有幾真實先推俾人睇啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有d傻西會信咩老母個朋友講<br />\n邊個再信就真係屌到你老母西反皮<br />\n<br />\n示意圖: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0B7NELP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0B7NELP.png&h=afb8fec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人你地全球智商排名好高<br />\n咪撚再信fake news <br />\n動動腦，轉轉彎。我阿姨個朋友都識啦<br />\n<br />\n五<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大訴求缺一不可<br />\n八月五我罷工<br />\n屌你老母林慧韡</span></span>"},{"pid":"e2094e4fcfb583565148bcadaab8396848c2f9e3","tid":1395751,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABmuS6B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABmuS6B.png&h=747c5c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa54e497da0cf72f47288ac518ff4d469c4279ba","tid":1395751,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:31:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"099a993a8f636ecc9327b45347dd39ce8b0fd5c6","tid":1395751,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:32:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7351b8a865cae13495345fb7d666a257ce033b4e","tid":1395751,"uid":50483,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:32:24.000Z","msg":"個POST主已經講左唔係義載 係自己call uber<br />\n咁uber應該會有個個司機既資料<br />\n<br /